node.text: Happy Birthday to my baby girl @choycebrown ❤️🎉. I don’t know how 20 years went by so fast😩. It feels like yesterday that I found out I was having a girl! You taught Mommy what it meant to fall in love with someone I had never met before!  You’ve taught me so much in the last 20 years and I’m so thankful to have grown with you not only as your Mom but your friend! Many days I would feel like I was getting it all wrong, but everyday you are showing me proof that I got a lot right! ❤️I’m so glad the Lord chose me to be your Mommy🙌🏾 I am so proud of the fearless young woman you have become and are becoming!! Keep being you, keep being true, keep standing for what you believe in, keep spreading love, keep spreading your wings, keep dreaming new dreams, keep living your dreams and most of all keep being free!!! I LOVE YOU babe!! Enjoy your day!! #happybirthday #20yearsold #choycebrown #Mommysgirl

node.text:
OMG family, I been working so much that I forgot today August 1st  is my  VEGAN ANNIVERSARY!🎉 
4 years ago today after being sick for 1 year and 7 months, I started a 30 day vegan challenge and never went back!!!! My health and life changed forever 🙌🏾🙌🏾🙌🏾.. I’m so glad I decided I was worth trying it for 30 days!!! OOHHH GOD I THANK YOU!!!!! 🙌🏾🙌🏾🙌🏾. Family we are WORTH giving ourselves a chance to change, to heal, to live, to be happy, to feel good, and we are certainly worth giving our all to a 30 day challenge that just might change our life!! So whatever it is that you are going thru give yourself 30 days of trying everyday to improve it❤️. Let my journey be your inspiration!  I believe in you!!! Love y’all!! #happyanniversary #vegananniversary #tabithabrown #4years
